    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tires screeching, black-smoke exhaust, and the smell of burned rubber. <strong>The Motorhead Pack is made for car, truck, and motorcycle enthusiasts</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spoiler alert: Lots of new spoilers! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We also got four new muscle-car skins: Matte, Carbon Fibre, Metallic, Iridescent - to really make that racer pop - complete it with the Race Driver Suit or Trucker Outfit. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take a look at all the new supercar stuff coming with the Motorhead Pack:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >New Block Skins</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Matte</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carbon Fibre</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Metallic</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Iridescent</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >New Costumes</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race Driver Suit (Advertisements/Logos)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trucker Outfit</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >New Blocks</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Racing</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stacked Front Wing Spoiler</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2x6x1 Back Wing Spoiler</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2x5x3 Halo Driving Seat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Racing Hinge</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Car</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supercar Spoiler 3x8x1</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Popup Light</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Small Fender 3x2x1</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Medium Fender 5x3x1</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short Car Hood</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Long Car Hood</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Truck</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Large suspension straight</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Large Fender 7x5x2 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Large Truck Exhaust</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>General</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Car Seat (Steering Wheel On/Off)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dashboard/Microfigure Chirpo</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dashboard/Microfigure Character</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tinted Smoke Generator</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >New Decals</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >License Plate </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Company Logos</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Emissive Lights</p></li></ul>",
